info.name: tumblr - Portal Icons
info.description: NOTE: As of 01.01.2013 this style will no longer be supported. Replaces the default New Post iconbar with Portal icons. Best used with the Dashboard Theme-Aperture Science style created by Celestialcow. NOTE: Images are embedded in the style as data URI, so the style shouldn't "disappear" until tumblr makes one of its many revisions :)
